root causes(in ordre of reality)

batching stops working
batch.size too small -> many tiny rquests
linger.ms = 0 -> no time to form batches

poor batching = low throughput

slow achnowledgments

acks=all waits for all replicas
isr shrinking or slow follower
leader waiting too long

slow acks = slow producer

compression disabled or misconfigured 

no compression -> huge network usage
under load, network becomes bottleneck

use lz4, snappy, szfd

broker disk i/o saturation
disk can't flush fast enough
page cache pressure
high write latency

producer slows becuase brokers can't keep up

network bottlenecks
packet drops 
high latency
saturated bandwidth

